room_title: Escape room "Da Vinci's Study" by Escape Of A Lifetime in New York
room_description: Leonardo Da Vinci was one the greatest minds the world has ever known. He invented, painted, sculpted and did so many things that we are still trying to figure out. You have stumbled upon a secret room that appears to have been occupied by the great maestro. Use the clues and puzzles he has left to uncover an unpublished manuscript. Can you steal the manuscript and escape undetected?
